Richard Boorman is the head of communications at Showmax and has been with the company since its launch in 2015. Showmax has shown strong growth over the last three years and has made many improvements to its streaming service. We are giving you an opportunity to ask Richard anything about Showmax. He will select 10 questions to answer, and everyone whose questions are selected will get a cool prize from MyBroadband. To take part in the discussion and post a question, visit the MyBroadband forum link below. Please post your questions before 12:00 on 13 June 2018.